OL,3,C'Hard and embarrassing to admit':
OL,4,CUnpaid carers struggling to make ends
OL,5,Cmeet
OL,7,FWith thousands of unpaid carers now
OL,8,Fliving in poverty, one father in North
OL,9,FYorkshire spoke to Jennie Henry about
OL,10,Fthe increasing financial strain he is
OL,11,Ffacing while caring for his wife and
OL,12,Fson
OL,14,FA father who cares for his disabled
OL,15,Fwife and son says it is "hard and
OL,16,Fembarrassing to admit" that he is
OL,17,Fstruggling to make ends meet.
