OL,3,C'Hard and embarrassing to admit':
OL,4,CUnpaid carers struggling to make ends
OL,5,Cmeet
OL,7,FDarren Romanus, from Sinnington, near
OL,8,FPickering, in North Yorkshire, cares
OL,9,Ffor his wife Carole and son Tyler who
OL,10,Fboth have disabilities.
OL,12,FWith increasing numbers of unpaid
OL,13,Fcarers now living in poverty,
OL,14,Faccording to a national survey, Darren
OL,15,Ftold ITV Tyne Tees that life was
OL,16,Fbecoming more difficult financially
OL,17,Fpeople like him are in need of support.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
