OL,3,C'Hard and embarrassing to admit':
OL,4,CUnpaid carers struggling to make ends
OL,5,Cmeet
OL,7,F"It's hard and it's embarrassing to
OL,8,Factually admit, but something needs to
OL,9,Fbe done," he said. "We've only just
OL,10,Ftransferred over to Universal Credit.
OL,11,FI get #81.90 a week for carer's
OL,12,Fallowance.
OL,14,F"They class the carer's allowance as
OL,15,Fincome, they take that off us once a
OL,16,Fmonth. We now don't get all our rent
OL,17,Fpaid, we don't get all the council tax
OL,18,Fpaid.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
