OL,3,C'Hard and embarrassing to admit':
OL,4,CUnpaid carers struggling to make ends
OL,5,Cmeet
OL,7,FAnd of the nation's carers surveyed,
OL,8,F61% are worried about living costs and
OL,9,Fmanaging in the future.
OL,11,FDarren is just one of more than 53,000
OL,12,Funpaid carers in North Yorkshire, and
OL,13,Fhis story is not uncommon.
OL,15,FCarer's UK says that while so many
OL,16,Fcarers are living in poverty, on a
OL,17,Fwhole are saving the economy in
OL,18,FEngland and Wales an estimated #162
OL,19,Fbillion a year.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
