OL,3,C'Hard and embarrassing to admit':
OL,4,CUnpaid carers struggling to make ends
OL,5,Cmeet
OL,7,FThe impact on carers is not just
OL,8,Ffinancial with the charity's national
OL,9,Fsurvey showing that it also affects
OL,10,Ftheir health and wellbeing.
OL,12,FHelen Walker, the CEO of Carer's UK,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We're finding that carers are
OL,14,Fin an extraordinarily difficult
OL,15,Fposition with their finances and
OL,16,Fthat's then having a knock-on effect
OL,17,Fwith their mental health, with their
OL,18,Fwellbeing, explained
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
