OL,3,C'Hard and embarrassing to admit':
OL,4,CUnpaid carers struggling to make ends
OL,5,Cmeet
OL,7,F"They're cutting back on social
OL,8,Finteraction with their family and
OL,9,Ffriends. That means that they're
OL,10,Fbecoming more isolated."
OL,12,FThe Government has said it is looking
OL,13,Fat a reform of the social care system.
OL,15,FIn a statement, it said: "Our country
OL,16,Fwould grind to a halt without the
OL,17,Fmillions of carers who provide care
OL,18,Fand continuity of support for
OL,19,Fvulnerable people every day.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
