OL,3,C'Hard and embarrassing to admit':
OL,4,CUnpaid carers struggling to make ends
OL,5,Cmeet
OL,7,F"We recognise the challenges they are
OL,8,Ffacing and we are determined to
OL,9,Fprovide unpaid carers with the support
OL,10,Fthey deserve. We are working on long-
OL,11,Fterm reform of the social care system
OL,12,Fto improve support for all."
OL,14,FHowever, things remain difficult for
OL,15,Ffamilies like Darren's and the
OL,16,Fpressure is only likely to increase as
OL,17,Fwinter approaches.
OL,19,FBut, he said, giving up is not an
OL,20,Foption.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
